till the middle of the night.

57
00:04:01,997 --> 00:04:02,957
If he can't come,

58
00:04:02,957 --> 00:04:04,677
he should at least explain it.

59
00:04:05,277 --> 00:04:07,638
How come Young Lord is so arrogant?

60
00:04:07,997 --> 00:04:09,797
Even if you are pretending
to play hard to get,

61
00:04:09,918 --> 00:04:12,598
y-you need to show up at least.

62
00:04:12,797 --> 00:04:15,957
