until he lost his voice.

156
00:10:09,357 --> 00:10:10,518
Didn't they drive him away?

157
00:10:10,717 --> 00:10:13,717
He refused to leave,
saying he must see you one last time.

158
00:10:14,158 --> 00:10:15,518
He almost alarmed His Highness.

159
00:10:17,357 --> 00:10:18,798
Li Tengyun.

160
00:10:21,237 --> 00:10:24,957
Young Lord, I had previously not
lived up to your expectations.

161
00:10:25,078 --> 00:10:27,438
But I guarantee
there won't be a next time.

162
