701
00:36:32,518 --> 00:36:34,157
but they always
keep you in their hearts.

702
00:36:35,117 --> 00:36:36,838
This is what they are supposed to do.

703
00:36:37,117 --> 00:36:38,358
This is what it means to be a family.

704
00:36:43,757 --> 00:36:44,958
Aren't they the earrings I gave you?

705
00:36:44,998 --> 00:36:47,637
Yes, I've put them on. Look pretty?

706
00:36:47,637 --> 00:36:48,637
I have such a good taste.

707
00:36:56,438 --> 00:37:02,838
About going to Dali,

708
00:37:04,038 --> 00:37:06,558
I thought it over carefully.

709
00:37:09,757 --> 00:37:11,078
You can consider it.

710
00:37:15,518 --> 00:37:18,597
Mr. Lu, now I

711
00:37:18,958 --> 00:37:21,398
